title: Education Incorporated
filterKeywords: eduinc education incorporated boutique school jax gershom aitchison teach learn
description:
EduInc is a registered, affordable, IEB Private School teaching grades 4 to 12 with 10 children per class.

Choosing the right school for your child is one of the biggest responsibilites of being a parent. This podcast channel will give you some insight into how EduInc operates and communicates with its community.
